description:
Diners.Drive-Ins.and.Dives.S18E12.Family.Time.PDTV.x264-JIVE

  This trip, Guy's visiting some families keeping it real in the kitchen.
In Nashville, the husband/wife duo taking to the streets in their
gourmet food truck with unique versions of the good ol' grilled
cheese sammie. Around the corner in the Sylvan Park area 
of Nashville, a totally authentic Italian spot staying true to 
grandma's recipes with their namesake lasagna and lamb 
shanks. And in Kansas City, Mo., the sibling-owned Chinese
joint sharing some of their family traditions with dishes like 
chili pepper wontons and firebird chicken.
